Designers and Explorers

About Britt

I received my first digital camera at the age of 10, and I have been exploring the world of digital imaging. Recording and finding beauty has become a habit for me. A lots of interesting works has been created including design, photography and video clips.

 

 I studied in the Communication Leadership program at the University of Washington now, constantly exploring the relationship between Communication, leadership, and design.

​

Hope you like my work! Contact me here! Brittdu@uw.edu
